                            <comment id="17189719" author="dongjoon" created="Wed, 2 Sep 2020 21:29:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you for reporting, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=igreenfi&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;igreenfi&quot;&gt;igreenfi&lt;/a&gt;. I also confirm this regression.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17189720" author="dongjoon" created="Wed, 2 Sep 2020 21:31:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cloud_fan&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cloud_fan&quot;&gt;cloud_fan&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=smilegator&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;smilegator&quot;&gt;smilegator&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17190331" author="sandeep.katta2007" created="Thu, 3 Sep 2020 17:42:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cloud_fan&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cloud_fan&quot;&gt;cloud_fan&lt;/a&gt;&#160;and&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=smilegator&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;smilegator&quot;&gt;smilegator&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I did some analysis on this, it is because as a part of&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-30009&quot; title=&quot;Replace Ordering.Double with Ordering.Double.TotalOrdering&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPARK-30009&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPARK-30009&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; org.apache.spark.util.Utils.nanSafeCompareDoubles is replaced with java.lang.Double.compare. Same can be confirmed from the codegen code, I have attached those for referrence.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you see the implementation of&#160;java.lang.Double.compare&lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;b&gt;java.lang.Double.compare(-0.0, 0.0) &amp;lt; 0 evaluates to true&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;java.lang.Double.compare(0.0, -0.0) &amp;lt; 0 evaluates to false&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17190333" author="sandeep.katta2007" created="Thu, 3 Sep 2020 17:48:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So it&apos;s edge case scenario, how should we fix it or we can leave it as limitation ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17190543" author="dongjoon" created="Fri, 4 Sep 2020 05:03:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you for analysis, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=sandeep.katta2007&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;sandeep.katta2007&quot;&gt;sandeep.katta2007&lt;/a&gt;. Also, cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=srowen&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;srowen&quot;&gt;srowen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17190637" author="apachespark" created="Fri, 4 Sep 2020 09:05:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User &apos;cloud-fan&apos; has created a pull request for this issue:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/29647&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/29647&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17190639" author="cloud_fan" created="Fri, 4 Sep 2020 09:06:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for your analysis, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=sandeep.katta2007&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;sandeep.katta2007&quot;&gt;sandeep.katta2007&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think we need to add back the `OrderingUtil` to implement custom compare methods to take care of 0.0 vs -0.0. I&apos;ve opened a PR for it:&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/29647&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/29647&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17191933" author="dongjoon" created="Tue, 8 Sep 2020 03:45:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Issue resolved by pull request 29647&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/29647&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/29647&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
